code: private EnumSet<Option> asEnumSet(Option[] options) {     if (options == null || options.length == 0) {         return EnumSet.noneOf(Option.class).     }     return EnumSet.copyOf(Arrays.asList(options)). }

comment: /**  * Returns a set of options that are understood by the {@link CommandRunner}.  * @return the options understood by the runner  */
code: /**  * Returns a set of options that are understood by the {@link CommandRunner}.  * @return the options understood by the runner  */ public Set<Option> getOptions() {     return Collections.unmodifiableSet(this.options). }
